{{Youmay|the Naboo squadron|[[Alpha Flight (Galactic Republic)|Alpha Flight]], the Galactic Republic squadron}}
'''Alpha Flight''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] that was based on the placid [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] as part of the [[Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps/Legends|Naboo Royal Space Fighter Corps]]. At some point in his career, [[Ric Olié/Legends|Ric Olié]] was a member of the unit.<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Characters">[[The New Essential Guide to Characters]]</ref>

